{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 272.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would say they need bricklayers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Fine, bricklayers?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm a bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How hard is it to lay bricks, especially I-- we used to manufacture bricks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they took you to unload cement trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I figured, you-- you want to build?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, you got to unload the cement trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was a very hard job because we weren't strong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We-- we-- we were weak people in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so for-- for about the next, I'd say three, four months, I worked at the-- at the Bauhof commander, which means unloading cars of cement.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "During that time, my brother took ill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had a terrible infection in one of the-- his toes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, the Germans loved experimentation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, they took him into the hospital and I guess he made it and they-- but I didn't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At night-- not at night, there was a curfew, but in wintertime especially or early spring-- [DRINKS] --I remember taking a candle so maybe he could look down.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because a lot of us prisoners, I mean, we had someone in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we-- so to find out if they're still alive or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we took a candle-- we got some candles, don't ask me where I got a candle-- but anyhow-- and I went and lit the candle so he can see me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't see him at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He recognized me and finally, I found him, he was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what they have done is they experimented really on him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They have cut his-- they split his toe, actually, into the big toe, one of his legs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they applied certain things and actually, he made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
